<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="a19Jul1935"><font color="red">19 July 1935</font> <i>NLHW</i> (from Paul L&eacute;on to Harriet Weaver):  The third part is practically finished. All the additions have been done on loose sheets during the four weeks of respite Mrs Joyce was able to influence him to have after the bad state he had been in had passed and the news from the Jolases came. The first part is as you know with the publishers.  </div>
